listing_description:
Lakeview Luxury Apartment in Uttara Dhaka, Bangladesh. It is situated 1.4 km from Uttara Center Metro Station and 13 km from Hazrat Shahjalal International Airport.  

Fully furnished Air-conditioned apartment comes with 1 bedroom, 3 bathrooms with geyser, 1 dressing room, bed linen, towels, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a dining area, a well equipped kitchen with a fridge, and a balcony with lake views.

As per the govt. regulations we took guests copy of NID/passport.
